# CHEAT-SHEET

| You want to… | Do this |
|---|---|
| Run today's audit | Invoke this prompt with no mode. |
| Re-run later same day | Same invocation — findings append to today's file. |
| Audit a single subtree | `SCOPE=services/auth/` (or "audit only services/auth"). |
| Approve work for the agent | Edit `status` to `APPROVED` on items where `assignee=AGENT`. |
| Preview a fix without committing state | `MODE=execute DRY_RUN=true`. |
| Have the agent implement approved work | `MODE=execute`. |
| Permanently decline a finding | Set `status` to `WONT_DO`. It writes to `wont-do.json` and never re-appears. |
| Defer to next sprint | Set `status` to `DEFERRED`. |
| Audit history of a finding | Read `history[]` on the item, or grep `transitions.jsonl` by `id`. |
| Power a dashboard | Consume `state/index.json` + daily `.json` mirrors + `transitions.jsonl`. |
